<DocsLayout title="ports" section="commands">
  <h1>ports</h1>
  <p class="lead">Show allocated host ports.</p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <pre><code>docktree ports [flags]</code></pre>
  <p>Reads from the port registry to show which host ports were allocated for each service in the current worktree.</p>

  <h2>Flags</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Flag</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>-a, --all</code></td><td>Show ports for all worktree instances</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Examples</h2>
  <pre><code>docktree ports</code></pre>
  <pre><code>  web    → 127.0.0.1:41001
  db     → 127.0.0.1:41002
  redis  → 127.0.0.1:41003</code></pre>
  <pre><code>docktree ports --all</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
